{
  "stem": "5371.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, the next day he brought me a ladies' gold watch.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I gave him-- to the kapo, my kapo-- I gave him the watch.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, good enough, in the evening, he came back, and he brought me the death sentence.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said to me, you've got a new lease on life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not that we knew I'm going to survive, you know, that I knew I'm going to survive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But at least I knew I'm back alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was down to maybe, I don't know, 85, 90 pounds, because I didn't eat whatever they gave me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So then, you know, you always hope.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I worked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then they transferred us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Being that we worked in between Auschwitz and Birkenau, they transferred us to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I worked in a strictly Polish kommando.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was a Polish group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I was the only Jew there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I heard a lot of, you know, remarks about Jews, you know, because most of the guys working in the same kommando or the same group were criminals, because they also had-- they all had green triangles, which meant that they were in prison before the war, you know, in prison.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were criminals.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "A few of them were political, also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I was a very good worker.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I slept in the barrack where they worked, so I didn't have to work on Sunday, because Jews had to work even Sundays.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They used to take the Jews out on Sunday, and they really didn't work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was they make them carry stones from one place and putting the stones back in the other place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That's what they used to do on Sundays.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Otherwise, during the week they worked on different places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went through several selections by Mengele.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
